OL,4,Chighlights Guernsey's housing crisis
OL,6,FIn some instances, individuals have
OL,7,Fstayed in the pods for up to a week.
OL,9,FGraham Merfield, Chair of Caritas,
OL,10,Ftold ITV News: "We've had some people
OL,11,Fwho are ex-offenders using them - some
OL,12,Fpeople who have been sofa surfing and
OL,13,Fhave no other accommodation".
OL,15,FHe continues: "The bad news is that
OL,16,Fpeople need to use them - they have
OL,17,Fnowhere else to go."
