OL,3,CDemand for emergency sleeping pods
OL,4,Chighlights Guernsey's housing crisis
OL,6,FThe pods, which cost the charity an
OL,7,Festimated #20,000, are managed based
OL,8,Fon need, with a short waiting list
OL,9,Favailable where possible.
OL,11,FWhile the pods do not offer a long-
OL,12,Fterm housing solution, Mr Merfield
OL,13,Fbelieves demand from the island's
OL,14,Fcommunity will only increase in the
OL,15,Fsummer months when more affordable
OL,16,Fwinter lets are no longer available.
