OL,3,CDemand for emergency sleeping pods
OL,4,Chighlights Guernsey's housing crisis
OL,6,FHe adds: "We know that during the
OL,7,Fsummer months, people are sleeping in
OL,8,Fbunkers, tents and cars, so we
OL,9,Fanticipate they'll be used more during
OL,10,Fthis period than in the winter."
OL,12,FThe pods also provide food vouchers
OL,13,Ffor use at Mill Street Community Cafe,
OL,14,Fwhere affordable food options are
OL,15,Favailable.
OL,17,FDavid Savident, the cafe's owner,
OL,18,Fcalled the homelessness situation in
OL,19,FGuernsey "shocking".
