OL,3,CDemand for emergency sleeping pods
OL,4,Chighlights Guernsey's housing crisis
OL,6,FHe continued: "I think more should be
OL,7,Fdone to help people who are at the
OL,8,Fother end of the scale, who are often
OL,9,Fin that situation due to no fault of
OL,10,Ftheir own."
OL,12,FThere are more than 1,000 islanders
OL,13,Fliving without secure housing,
OL,14,Faccording to the 2024 Guernsey Annual
OL,15,FBetter Life Indicators Report.
OL,17,FHowever, exact data on the number of
OL,18,Fpeople experiencing homelessness is
OL,19,Fnot yet known, prompting the States to
OL,20,Fback a survey to get a clearer picture
OL,21,Fof the issue.
